{{Spanish name 2|Echenique|Robba}} {{Infobox officeholder | name = Pablo Echenique Robba | image = Premios Goya 2018 - Pablo Echenique y Pablo Iglesias (cropped).jpg | alt = | caption = Pablo Echenique Robba in 2018. | birth_name = |office1 = Member of the [[Aragonese Corts]] |term_start1 = 18 June 2015 |term_end1 = |constituency1 = [[Zaragoza (province)|Zaragoza]] |office2 = [[Member of the European Parliament]] |term_start2 = 1 July 2014 |term_end2 = 14 March 2015 |constituency2 = [[Spain (European Parliament constituency)|Spain]] | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1978|08|28}} | birth_place = [[Rosario, Santa Fe]], [[Argentina]] Height: 1'56 m | death_date = | death_place = | nationality = | other_names = | occupation = Physicist and politician | known_for = | alma_mater = [[Universidad de Zaragoza]] | education = Doctorate in Physics | party = [[Podemos (Spanish political party)|Podemos]] | spouse = María Alejandra Nelo Bazán }} '''Pablo Echenique Robba'''<ref>[http://podemos.info/candidatos/pablo-echenique-robba/ Pablo in Podemos page] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222032907/http://podemos.info/candidatos/pablo-echenique-robba/ |date=2015-02-22 }}</ref> (born 28 August 1978 in [[Rosario, Santa Fe]], [[Argentina]]) is an Argentine-born Spanish physicist and politician. He was one of the five [[Member of the European Parliament|MEP]]s elected by [[Podemos (Spanish political party)|Podemos]] in the [[European Parliament election, 2014 (Spain)|2014 European Parliament election]], and is currently a member of the [[Aragonese Corts]].<ref>{{cite news|first= Eduardo |last= López Alonso |title= Podemos, el partido revelación de Pablo Iglesias |url= http://www.elperiodico.com/es/noticias/europa/podemos-partido-revelacion-pablo-iglesias-3282574 |work= [[El Periódico de Catalunya]] |date= 26 May 2014 |accessdate= 3 July 2014 }} {{es icon}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first= Luis |last= Giménez San Miguel |title= Los otros diputados de Podemos |url= http://www.publico.es/523420/los-otros-diputados-de-podemos |work= [[Público (España)|Público]] |date= 28 May 2014 |accessdate= 3 July 2014 }} {{es icon}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title= Echenique Robba, Pablo |url= http://www.cortesaragon.es/Ficha-Personal.1399.0.html?&tx_parlament_pi5%5BshowUid%5D=1963 |work= [[Aragonese Corts]] |accessdate= 29 October 2016 }} {{es icon}}</ref>
As a scientist, he holds a position at the [[Spanish National Research Council]] in [[Zaragoza]] (CSIC).<ref name="elmundo01">{{Cite web |url=http://www.elmundo.es/cronica/2014/06/01/53898565268e3e54468b456b.html |title=El otro Pablo de Podemos |first=Martín |last=Mucha |date=1 June 2014 |publisher=Crónica de [[El Mundo (España)|El Mundo]] |accessdate=26 June 2014}} {{es icon}}</ref>
